snippet.title: Top 10 weirdest dogs on Earth that will make you laugh hard - Funny dog compilation
snippet.description:
Dogs can be so strange and weird sometimes. They make funny sounds and noises, have strange ways of playing, funny reflexes, tricks, they are spinning, sneezing and so on. But they are still cute and the best! I'm sure this compilation will make you laugh pretty hard ;)  Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
